    <item>
      <title>韩国举行紧急会议以回应美国关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统公布了对贸易伙伴的关税之后，韩国的临时领导人汉德鸭 - 苏敦促官员们积极与美国进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</guid>
