    <item>
      <title>越南魅力攻势未能避免46％的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南部署了特朗普政府的攻击性攻势，削减了进口税，并发誓要购买更多的大型美国产品来保护其贸易依赖的经济，但未能避免避免白宫宣布的最大关税之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的出口机以至少54％的特朗普关税袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国在几乎所有中国产品上都以有史以来最大的关税加息袭击了中国，这使总税款至少达到54％，这一举动可能会使中国货物送往世界上最大的经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-hikes-china-tariffs-to-at-least-54-in-blow-to-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:22:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>UC教职联盟在反犹太主义调查中与联邦传票作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uc-faculty-union-fights-federal-subpoena-in-antisemitism-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表成千上万加州大学教职员工的工会表示，它正在反对该机构遵守与对反犹太主义指控的调查有关的联邦传票的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uc-faculty-union-fights-federal-subpoena-in-antisemitism-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:15:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔巴内斯猛击王牌对澳大利亚的关税为“糟糕的决定”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/australia-pm-says-10-us-tariff-a-poor-decision-won-t-respond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）表示，美国宣布对澳大利亚商品的10％关税是一个“糟糕的决定”，同时说他不会以互惠征税的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/australia-pm-says-10-us-tariff-a-poor-decision-won-t-respond</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:54:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent在5月或6月的债务限制“警告轨道”上向我们发出信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bessent-signals-us-on-debt-limit-warning-track-for-may-or-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）表示，联邦政府有可能在5月或6月及时及时履行其所有付款义务的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bessent-signals-us-on-debt-limit-warning-track-for-may-or-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:52:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税无所不包；亚洲和欧洲遭受更大的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统正在对全球贸易伙伴征收关税，这是他对全球经济体系的最大攻击，他长期以来一直为不公平而感到不公平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-says-he-s-signing-executive-order-on-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:16:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
